snippet.title: Unboxing New Spiderman Battery-Powered Ride On Super Car 6V Test Drive Park Playtime Fun Ckn Toys
snippet.description:
Hi guys today Spiderman will be unboxing and asemmbling this new super spiderman kids electric ride on 6 volt car.This would have to be our favourite car so far because it look so cool.
The Spider-Man Super Car features an open cockpit design for the ultimate Spider-Man riding experience! This Super Car has a Spider-Man water shooter to emulate the web throwing of the ultimate Spider-Man! This 6-volt Spider-Man Super Car is featured in a classic red and blue Spider-Man finish with graphics, freestyle doors for easy access to the drivers seat, exciting light-up hood lights and sound making horn!
We took it to the park for a test drive ,it run on a 6-volt battery so it is not as fast as our last Police car which is a 12-volt.But still perfect for this little Spiderman as he is only 4 years old.
We hope you enjoy this video and if you do please don't forget to subscribe.

snippet.title: Unboxing New Batman Battery-Powered Ride On Batmobile 6V Test Drive Park Playtime Fun Ckn Toys
snippet.description:
Hi guys today Batman will be unboxing and assembling this new super Batmobile kids electric power wheels ride on 6 volt car.This would have to be our new favourite car so far because it look so cool and we love Batman so much.
This Best Ride On Cars Batmobile 6V Battery Powered Car will thrill any young Bat-fan. The hard plastic body is emblazoned with Batman insignia on the hood, the sides, the seat and the fins. The kids' powered car has a headlight, center lights and a multicolor center light. It seats one child, and the maximum weight capacity is 40 lbs. The kids' toy car can operate outdoors on hard surface roads or on grass. The maximum speed is 2 to 3 mph. It has a seat belt for safety and a remote control option for supervision by adults.
We took it to the park for a test drive ,it runs on a 6-volt battery so it is not as fast as our Police car which is a 12-volt.But still perfect for this little Batman as he is only 4 years old.
We hope you enjoy this video and if you do please don't forget to subscribe.

snippet.title: Unboxing Kid Trax Disney Pixar Finding Dory Submarine 6 Volt Battery Powered Ride-On Toy Car Ckn
snippet.description:
Hi guys, today we are so excited to be unboxing and testing this cool Kid Trax Disney Pixar Finding Dory 6 volt battery powered ride-on submarine. They found Nemo, and now they need your help finding Dory too! Explore the deep depths of backyard fun in a Disney Pixar 6 volt Finding Dory Submarine by Kid Trax. Kids will love motoring around and spying above sea level with the working periscope that is removable and usable apart from the vehicle. Their friends Nemo and Dory will always be at their side. This little submarine that drives like a car will make all in its wake smile. The propeller in the rear spins as the motor pushes the sub forwards at a top speed of 2.5 miles per hours and it will spin the opposite direction when the sub goes in reverse.
Please don't forget to subscribe to Ckn Toys if you enjoy this video.

snippet.title: POLICE CAR Ride On Racing Fun With CKN Toys
snippet.description:
Today we are playing with my new 12V ride on battery powered Police car. We are going to build this police car and then take it out to race and have some fun playtime with our friends.
Officer Speedy reporting for duty. The Dodge Pursuit Police Car Ride-on Toy from Kid Trax was made for imaginative little ones. With tons of realistic features like a working megaphone, flashing lights and real siren sounds, your trooper-in-training will want to spend all day looking for law breakers.
Thank you for watching CKN Toys.
